premise_source_doc_sentence: Matthew `` Matt '' Flynn  (  born May 23 , 1975  )  is an American musician .
Karl Johan Schuster  (  -LSB- ˈjuːˈan ˈɧʏstɛr -RSB- ; born 1 February 1985  )  , known professionally as Shellback , is a Swedish songwriter , record producer , and musician .
In 2010 , PJ Morton auditioned to be a touring keyboardist and backing vocalist of Maroon 5 and joined the band .

Morton became an official member when he filled-in for Jesse Carmichael  (  who took a temporary break from performing with the group to focus on his studies  )  from 2012 to 2014 and , as Carmichael came back to the band in 2014 , the latest  (  and current  )  line-up was made  (  it is also the first Maroon 5 line-up that consists of six official members  )  .
In 2001 , guitarist James Valentine joined and the band changed the name to Maroon 5 .
